metaInfos.name: x_gromacs_frame_sequence_bond_energy
metaInfos.description: Array containing the values of the bond_energy along this sequence of frames (i.e., a trajectory, a frame is one section_single_configuration_calculation). If not all frames have a value the indices of the frames that have a value are stored in frame_sequence_bond_energy_frames.
